00f4ng n\u00ean th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, v\u00f2ng vo tr\u01b0\u1edbc truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-seeding.html\/#Buoc_4_Cach_ly_xu_ly_thong_tin_trong_khung_hoang\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: C\u00e1ch ly, x\u1eed l\u00fd th\u00f4ng tin trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: C\u00e1ch ly, x\u1eed l\u00fd th\u00f4ng tin trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-seeding.html\/#Buoc_5_Dat_loi_ich_cong_dong_len_tren\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: \u0110\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean tr\u00ean\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: \u0110\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean tr\u00ean<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-seeding.html\/#Buoc_6_Rut_ra_bai_hoc_sau_khung_hoang_truyen_thong\" title=\"B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: R\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc sau kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: R\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc sau kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-seeding.html\/#Tai_sao_ban_nen_lua_chon_dich_vu_seeding_cua_Achaumedia\" title=\"T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 seeding c\u1ee7a Achaumedia?\">T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 seeding c\u1ee7a Achaumedia?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Seeding<\/strong> l\u00e0 g\u00ec, x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong forum seeding l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u201cb\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m\u201d bi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng doanh s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. V\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft h\u00f4m nay <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/\"><strong>Achaumedia<\/strong><\/a> s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11906\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-3-300x259.jpg\" alt=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Seeding l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"691\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-3-300x259.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-3-768x663.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-3.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_Seeding_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Seeding l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Seeding l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a Digital Marketing \u2013 ti\u1ebfng Anh mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201cgieo m\u1ea7m\u201d. Trong Marketing, n\u1ebfu coi n\u1ed9i dung l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gieo m\u1ea7m (ph\u00e1t t\u00e1n) v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ea3y m\u1ea7m, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. Seeding l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a marketing online s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p>Seeding \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c Marketing Online ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean PR qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec c\u00e1c seeder \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n th\u00f4ng tin m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o. Nhi\u1ec1u khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb c\u00e1c seeder m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft, c\u1ee9 \u0111inh ninh r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111ang ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u, ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ngu\u1ed3n tin theo \u00fd m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-viet-book-bai-tren-bao.html\/\"><em><strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft Book b\u00e0i tr\u00ean b\u00e1o v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bao-gia-dich-vu-viet-bai-thue-theo-yeu-cau.html\/\"><em><strong>B\u00e1o gi\u00e1 D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i thu\u00ea theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ban_chat_cua_nhiem_vu_cua_dich_vu_seeding_la_gi\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 seeding l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Thu h\u00fat m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 l\u1ed3ng gh\u00e9p nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m\/ d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<li>Khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch trao \u0111\u1ed5i, k\u00edch th\u00edch kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng lan truy\u1ec1n, t\u1ea1o cho h\u1ecd ni\u1ec1m tin, t\u0103ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/li>\n<li>T\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean top cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, thu h\u00fat l\u01b0\u1ee3t traffic t\u1eeb Google th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c topic khi\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin lan truy\u1ec1n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n<\/li>\n<li>T\u0103ng t\u00ednh nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd<\/li>\n<li>T\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u nhanh h\u01a1n, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ea1o ngu\u1ed3n backlink ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao l\u00e0m t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean cho c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c SEO c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11907\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-300x142.png\" alt=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Seeding, x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"380\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-300x142.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-1024x486.png 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-768x364.png 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_dich_vu_seeding\"><\/span><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 seeding\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Seeding d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh AISAS, m\u1ed9t m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh theo d\u00f5i h\u00e0nh vi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u201cc\u1ef1c th\u1ecbnh\u201d nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y nay do Dentsu t\u1ea1o ra. M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia ra th\u00e0nh 5 ch\u1eef \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi t\u1eebng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau A (Attention), I (Interest), S (Search), A (Action), S (Share). Th\u00eam v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh 3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ch\u00ednh sau \u0111\u00e2y:<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giai_doan_1_Nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_Awareness_stage\"><\/span><strong>Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 1: Nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u (Awareness stage)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1eb7t x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u1eb7c m\u1edbi ra m\u1eaft th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n seeding, m\u1eabu Seeding n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 g\u00e2y s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 t\u00f2 m\u00f2 cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giai_doan_2_Gia_tang_gia_tri_cam_xuc_Emotion_Stage\"><\/span><strong>Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2: Gia t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea3m x\u00fac (Emotion Stage)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c seeder th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c m\u1eabu \u0111\u1ed1i tho\u1ea1i, th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn xoay quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, d\u1eabn c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. Theo kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Hosting Vi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ebft c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giai_doan_3_Hanh_dong_truc_tiep_Action_Stage\"><\/span><strong>Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 3: H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp (Action Stage)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eb1m bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng online th\u00e0nh offline. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a, seeder \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng share ho\u1eb7c mua h\u00e0ng<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11905\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-2-300x117.jpg\" alt=\"Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong forum seeding\" width=\"800\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-2-300x117.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-2-1024x400.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-2-768x300.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-2-1536x600.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-seeding-xu-ly-khung-hoang-truyen-thong-2.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Khung_hoang_truyen_thong_trong_forum_seeding\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong forum seeding<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Nhi\u1ec1u doanh nghi\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y h\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ee7i ro n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 quan qu\u00ean m\u1ea5t c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111ang \u00e2m \u1ec9 trong c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng, tr\u00ean c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n forum seeding, d\u1ea7n d\u1ea7n bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.<\/p>\n<p>L\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n x\u1ea3y ra ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea7m ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty khi c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ty hay s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m tr\u00ean c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n forum seeding. S\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty.<\/p>\n<p>Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng hay xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f2n th\u00f4ng tin x\u1ea5u th\u00ec b\u1ecb lan truy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t, \u0111\u01b0a ra h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1eed l\u00fd sai l\u1ea7m, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh, l\u00e0m cho kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng c\u00e0ng lan r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cac_buoc_xu_ly_khung_hoang_truyen_thong_cho_doanh_nghiep_trong_dich_vu_seeding\"><\/span><strong>C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 seeding<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7n l\u00ean m\u00f4t l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 6 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng:<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_1_Lap_team_xu_ly_khung_hoang\"><\/span><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: L\u1eadp team x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp ban x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng g\u1ed3m ban gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch ph\u00e1p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, tr\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u00f2ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u00f2ng PR, tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u01a1i x\u1ea3y ra kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng ban x\u1eed l\u00fd. Ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n cho kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_2_Hop_tac_voi_bao_chi_va_chinh_quyen_noi_kinh_doanh\"><\/span><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: H\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n n\u01a1i kinh doanh<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng theo m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra r\u00e0nh m\u1ea1ch theo m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean s\u1eb5n. H\u00e3y h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch l\u1eafng nghe v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u00f2a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ngay c\u1ea3 khi doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_3_Hay_phat_ngon_va_hanh_dong_mot_cach_nhat_quan\"><\/span><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: H\u00e3y ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>H\u00e3y ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"De_cong_dong_xem_rang_su_viec_dang_xay_ra_voi_doanh_nghiep_chi_mang_tinh_hien_tuong_chu_khong_thuoc_ve_ban_chat_thi_doanh_nghiep_can_phai_thuc_hien_xu_ly_khung_hoang_dong_bo_Dam_bao_moi_thu_thong_nhat_tu_khau_phat_ngon_cua_doanh_nghiep_cho_toi_cac_bien_phap_xu_ly_khung_hoang_Khong_nen_the_hien_tinh_than_tranh_ne_hua_hen_vong_vo_truoc_truyen_thong\"><\/span>\u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng xem r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t th\u00ec doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9. \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb kh\u00e2u ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p cho t\u1edbi c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh n\u00e9, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n, v\u00f2ng vo tr\u01b0\u1edbc truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_4_Cach_ly_xu_ly_thong_tin_trong_khung_hoang\"><\/span><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: C\u00e1ch ly, x\u1eed l\u00fd th\u00f4ng tin trong kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng x\u1ea3y ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, v\u00ec v\u1eady ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean ch\u1eb7n ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00fang lan r\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ed3ng minh khi x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u00e0o c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho v\u00e0o ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_5_Dat_loi_ich_cong_dong_len_tren\"><\/span><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: \u0110\u1eb7t l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean tr\u00ean<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>H\u00e3y l\u1ea5y l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng (kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng) l\u00e0m trung t\u00e2m trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. H\u00e3y t\u1ea1m b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_6_Rut_ra_bai_hoc_sau_khung_hoang_truyen_thong\"><\/span><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: R\u00fat ra b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc sau kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Sau ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng, h\u00e3y xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, t\u1eeb nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1edbi n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t k\u1ef9.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11719\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-booking-bao-chi-tp-hcm-3-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 booking b\u00e1o ch\u00ed tp hcm\" width=\"800\" height=\"451\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-booking-bao-chi-tp-hcm-3-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-booking-bao-chi-tp-hcm-3-1024x578.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-booking-bao-chi-tp-hcm-3-768x433.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-booking-bao-chi-tp-hcm-3-1536x866.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/06\/dich-vu-booking-bao-chi-tp-hcm-3.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tai_sao_ban_nen_lua_chon_dich_vu_seeding_cua_Achaumedia\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 seeding c\u1ee7a Achaumedia?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Achaumedia v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m tri\u1ec3n khai forum seeding v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nick tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi cao,<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u1edbn, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc:<\/li>\n<li>N\u1ed9i dung seeding kh\u00e1ch quan, c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn PR t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, v\u0103n phong v\u00f9ng mi\u1ec1n \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a t\u1ed1i \u01b0u SEO<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t topic c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb 25-35 nick t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, m\u1ed7i nick t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi 1 n\u0103m, nick c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0i tr\u0103m b\u00e0i, ch\u1ee9 TUY\u1ec6T \u0110\u1ed0I KH\u00d4NG l\u00e0m theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t topic ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5-6 nick m\u1edbi tinh, b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft l\u00e8o t\u00e8o r\u1ed3i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nhau c\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y KPI nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00ean l\u00e0m t\u1ef1 do kh\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<li>S\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u k\u00eanh m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i uy t\u00edn tr\u00ean Youtube, Facebook gi\u00fap t\u0103ng viral v\u00e0 k\u00e9o t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c cho topic<\/li>\n<li>Achaumedia CAM K\u1ebeT \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u00e0 &#8220;l\u1eb7n m\u1ea5t t\u0103m&#8221; nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u00ean nh\u1eadn l\u00e0m t\u1ef1 do kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Hy v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edch cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u00e0o, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 seeding n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch marketing c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, th\u00ec c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ki\u1e